snippet.title: CGR Trailers - FAR CRY: THE WILD EXPEDITION Far Cry Classic Trailer (UK)
snippet.description:
Far Cry: The Wild Expedition trailer. http://www.ClassicGameRoom.com
Shop CGR t-shirts and mugs! http://www.CGRstore.com

Classic Game Room's CGR Trailers presents a "Far Cry Classic" trailer for the FAR CRY: THE WILD EXPEDITION compilation from Ubisoft for the PC, PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 platforms. This collection brings together Far Cry, Far Cry 2, Far Cry 3 and Far Cry 3: Blood Dragon into one package. Enjoy!
